@eisig : We found the issue. It is caused by not properly shutting down a client which is opened in the filter-dupes path. 
Have a PR https://github.com/apache/incubator-hudi/pull/725 
We will merge it hopefully soon but meanwhile you can use this PR and try.

@amaranathv : From the commit, it looks like you are writing to local file system

file:/mapr/user/avenka23/delta-streamer/output7/2018/08/31/86f06040-14e7-4c0c-989b-72b2b59fe119-0_0-20-21_20190618132401.parquet

If you are running this in a cluster setup (docker/non-docker), the file might have been wriiten in some executor host's local file-system. Use hdfs or cloud storage.
